  "remarks": "JSC BTK Group is a Russian company specialising in uniforms and special clothing for military purposes. It is among the companies included in the register of organisations of the defence industry complex of the Ministry of Industry and Trade. JSC BTK Group delivers military clothing to the Russian Ministry of Defence and the National Guard of Russia (Rosgvardia), including for use in combat operations in Ukraine.",
